1
00:02:59,497 --> 00:03:02,000
Sudan...Africa...

2
00:03:03,335 --> 00:03:04,502
A strange place to me,

3
00:03:04,669 --> 00:03:06,671
Unknown language...unknown people...

4
00:03:15,221 --> 00:03:19,432
Having been a fisherman all my life,
it's not easy to learn new job.

5
00:03:22,227 --> 00:03:23,937
I found a good friend there.

6
00:03:24,145 --> 00:03:25,063
His name is Swamy.

7
00:03:25,688 --> 00:03:26,855
Like my Chinna!

8
00:03:29,067 --> 00:03:32,361
I hated this job but still I did.

9
00:03:41,161 --> 00:03:44,372
I separated fish from sea,
may be that was a sin,

10
00:03:45,789 --> 00:03:47,709
life too me away from sea.

11
00:03:47,876 --> 00:03:52,379
Oh no! Why do you always talk
about water, sea and fishes?

12
00:03:52,545 --> 00:03:54,465
What's so great about your place!

13
00:03:55,216 --> 00:03:55,883
Pani!

14
00:03:57,800 --> 00:04:01,470
People back in my village
too work in fields.

15
00:04:03,389 --> 00:04:04,515
This is different Pani.

16
00:04:04,765 --> 00:04:05,808
You can't understand.

17
00:04:07,102 --> 00:04:11,813
Buddy, the best thing I learnt
from you is smoking cigars.

18
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:12,981
Very good.

19
00:04:13,189 --> 00:04:15,901
Isn't it great?
That's special from my place.

20
00:04:16,067 --> 00:04:20,404
My only comfort is talking
to Pani once in week.

21
00:04:21,656 --> 00:04:23,407
I'm happy all that day.

22
00:04:24,074 --> 00:04:25,492
I'll sleep peacefully.

23
00:04:30,081 --> 00:04:33,668
Slowly I got used to the place
and the people there.

24
00:04:34,543 --> 00:04:36,002
All were like me, right?

25
00:04:39,798 --> 00:04:41,007
2 years!

26
00:04:43,093 --> 00:04:44,343
Somehow went by!

27
00:04:46,805 --> 00:04:48,223
I'm going back home.

28
00:04:48,973 --> 00:04:50,432
I'm going to meet my Pani.

29
00:04:51,184 --> 00:04:53,352
I'll sleep in the lap of Mother Sea.

30
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:12,995
How are you, Pani?

31
00:05:15,122 --> 00:05:16,206
How about you?

32
00:05:16,956 --> 00:05:18,041
Now I feel good!

33
00:05:21,002 --> 00:05:22,378
Just one more week to go, Maria!

34
00:05:22,545 --> 00:05:26,548
Two years went past somehow.

35
00:05:26,757 --> 00:05:29,468
But now a week appears much longer.

36
00:05:29,634 --> 00:05:33,305
You said it and I didn't, that's all.

37
00:05:33,889 --> 00:05:35,141
I'm coming Pani!

38
00:05:36,641 --> 00:05:37,935
Back to sea breeze,

39
00:05:38,769 --> 00:05:39,810
salt water,

40
00:05:40,603 --> 00:05:41,896
and you in my arms.

41
00:05:47,944 --> 00:05:50,822
First thing, I want to have is delicious
spicy gravy and rice prepared by you.

42
00:05:52,447 --> 00:05:53,490
Sure.

43
00:05:53,990 --> 00:05:56,826
Did you get my last letter?

44
00:05:59,454 --> 00:06:03,083
Got your 53rd letter...
and...got that also!

45
00:06:05,584 --> 00:06:07,753
Hey, don't send me anymore!

46
00:06:09,338 --> 00:06:10,923
Rest in person.

47
00:06:12,966 --> 00:06:14,509
Is it?

48
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:24,853
Yesupadam has announced to every person
in the village about our wedding.

49
00:06:27,105 --> 00:06:29,524
The only thing left is
to stitch your suit.

50
00:06:30,774 --> 00:06:34,694
Tell Yesupadam my size has changed
in the last two years.

51
00:06:34,862 --> 00:06:36,614
Let's get it done when I am back.

52
00:06:37,113 --> 00:06:39,115
I hope you are in the
size I can hug, right?

53
00:06:40,617 --> 00:06:41,285
What?

54
00:06:41,451 --> 00:06:43,703
I am running out of change.

55
00:06:44,329 --> 00:06:45,788
I need to get back to work.

56
00:06:46,581 --> 00:06:47,624
Shall I go?

57
00:06:49,041 --> 00:06:50,292
Shall I?

58
00:06:53,963 --> 00:06:57,216
Listen Maria, come back safely!

59
00:06:57,382 --> 00:06:59,133
Okay, see you.

60
00:07:52,516 --> 00:07:54,935
What is he saying?
- He thinks this is Dubai.

61
00:07:55,101 --> 00:07:57,603
Hey! This is not Dubai!
This is Africa!

62
00:07:57,771 --> 00:07:59,480
We have shed our blood
for two years.

63
00:07:59,648 --> 00:08:02,692
He has just arrived.
He will know as days go by.

64
00:08:07,906 --> 00:08:10,199
Hey Bald man, play some Telugu song.

65
00:08:10,365 --> 00:08:11,950
Hey uncle, play Hindi song,

66
00:08:12,117 --> 00:08:13,868
What Hindi song?

67
00:08:14,036 --> 00:08:16,204
You made Ravan with Shahrukh
competing with us,

68
00:08:16,372 --> 00:08:18,290
it flopped, right?
Why do you still insist on Hindi songs?

69
00:08:18,456 --> 00:08:21,918
A heart is sprouting inside iron...

70
00:08:22,084 --> 00:08:26,171
It is seeking kiss in love...

71
00:08:26,505 --> 00:08:29,299
Madrasi in Dharavi...I see you in Africa...
find them everywhere.

72
00:08:29,466 --> 00:08:30,509
Shut up, you nasty!

73
00:08:30,675 --> 00:08:33,220
You're with us unable to find
job anywhere, why still separate us?

74
00:08:33,386 --> 00:08:36,556
Sridevi is from South,
Hema Malini is from South,

75
00:08:36,724 --> 00:08:39,643
Silk Smitha is from South.
A.R.Rahman is from South.

76
00:08:39,809 --> 00:08:41,852
So is Sachin Tendulkar.

77
00:08:42,019 --> 00:08:44,355
Sorry! Tongue slip.

78
00:08:44,522 --> 00:08:46,524
Maria, isn't our place
foreign city to this place?

79
00:08:46,691 --> 00:08:47,649
Will you keep shut?

80
00:08:47,817 --> 00:08:51,153
Keeping shut always has
made it useless.

81
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:54,657
Your life is set,
you'll get married soon.

82
00:08:54,823 --> 00:08:57,909
You're feeling so much
for 2 years seeing a photo.

83
00:08:58,076 --> 00:09:02,663
But see, I'm feeling so much
for 4 girls in on photo.

84
00:09:02,831 --> 00:09:04,749
But still unable to trap even one!

85
00:09:04,916 --> 00:09:08,253
No use if you have the feeling,
it must come from that side too.

86
00:09:13,173 --> 00:09:14,424
My name is Maria.

87
00:09:15,384 --> 00:09:17,344
Maria means
the man who never dies!

88
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:22,139
As my name suggests…
I was arrogant and full of pride.

89
00:09:23,015 --> 00:09:25,017
Instead of salty air,
I got dust storm.

90
00:09:25,184 --> 00:09:27,060
Instead of dry fish,
I got tasteless meal.

91
00:09:28,229 --> 00:09:29,689
All my arrogance disappeared.

92
00:09:30,105 --> 00:09:33,442
There I was the king...
King of the sea.

93
00:09:55,671 --> 00:09:58,841
By catching the Tiger shark
Maria has brought pride to place.

94
00:09:59,006 --> 00:10:02,468
What his late father could not
20 years ago he did it now.

95
00:10:02,802 --> 00:10:04,596
You are the King of the sea.

96
00:10:04,763 --> 00:10:06,639
You've kept your father's pride!

97
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:14,479
Youth is swinging...

98
00:10:14,647 --> 00:10:18,817
Swinging amidst lashing waves...

99
00:10:34,664 --> 00:10:38,501
It's a garland of flowers...

100
00:10:38,668 --> 00:10:40,586
It has come seeking you...

101
00:10:40,754 --> 00:10:42,672
Oh my golden girl...

102
00:10:49,595 --> 00:10:51,764
Come my, dear...

103
00:11:31,509 --> 00:11:35,137
The golden girl gave her
beauty to me...

104
00:11:35,303 --> 00:11:39,390
She hid more beauty under her wings...

105
00:11:39,557 --> 00:11:43,144
She gives kiss for kiss...

106
00:11:43,562 --> 00:11:47,481
When you're with me smiling
time flies away...

107
00:11:47,649 --> 00:11:51,235
My cuckoo...my melody...
my golden girl...

108
00:11:51,402 --> 00:11:55,239
My moon...my jasmine...
my golden girl...

109
00:11:55,405 --> 00:11:59,158
My golden girl fills my life...

110
00:12:15,924 --> 00:12:18,468
Looks like you've stolen everything, Maria!

111
00:12:18,634 --> 00:12:20,761
Leave something for us too!

112
00:12:20,928 --> 00:12:23,889
Didn't find anyone else to pick up fight?

113
00:12:24,182 --> 00:12:25,265
Mind your work.

114
00:12:27,226 --> 00:12:30,771
He's the only guy refusing
to come to my way!

115
00:12:50,706 --> 00:12:52,332
In cool eyes...

116
00:12:52,958 --> 00:12:54,626
Under cool moonlight...

117
00:12:55,126 --> 00:12:56,211
One the wings of romance...

118
00:12:56,378 --> 00:12:58,297
Heart is having hiccups...

119
00:13:02,426 --> 00:13:06,596
Kiss me passionately on my cheeks...

120
00:13:06,763 --> 00:13:10,932
Make a bed of honey and love for me...

121
00:13:38,667 --> 00:13:40,502
Okay, come abroad.

122
00:13:44,714 --> 00:13:50,470
You're the lone man who rocks with the
spear fishing technique learnt over years.

123
00:13:50,635 --> 00:13:54,514
Buddy risks life to catch fish and
we enjoy eating food and drinking!

124
00:13:54,682 --> 00:13:55,932
I'm hungry, open the lunch box.

125
00:13:57,308 --> 00:13:58,684
Take this, buddy.

126
00:13:58,851 --> 00:13:59,769
He gives only cooked rice.

127
00:13:59,937 --> 00:14:01,855
This is mixed with love and wish.

128
00:14:02,022 --> 00:14:05,150
Is Maria yearning for it?

129
00:14:05,317 --> 00:14:08,443
Look, he always tells about you to Pani.

130
00:14:08,610 --> 00:14:11,697
He's delivering dialogue
about love and wish here.

131
00:14:11,864 --> 00:14:14,450
If he likes, he won't leave
without having it.

132
00:14:14,616 --> 00:14:16,951
If Maria doesn't like,
he'll never go after it.

133
00:14:17,119 --> 00:14:18,787
I too know that.

134
00:14:18,953 --> 00:14:23,625
Like NTR and Savithri...
like ANR and Jamuna...

135
00:14:23,792 --> 00:14:25,918
She's the perfect match for him like them.

136
00:14:26,086 --> 00:14:28,212
Buddy, shall I tell you a thing?
- Why not two?

137
00:14:28,379 --> 00:14:31,340
Buddy, I'm serious.
- Go ahead.

138
00:14:31,506 --> 00:14:35,135
What you don’t expect may never happen,
but what you expect will surely happen.

139
00:14:35,302 --> 00:14:38,471
Are you giving counter punch to mine?
I'll kick on your pot belly.

140
00:14:38,639 --> 00:14:39,889
If you kick on my belly...

141
00:14:40,057 --> 00:14:42,517
Nothing happened till now and
it'll not happen in future too.

142
00:14:42,683 --> 00:14:44,394
Got it? Shut up and mind your work.

143
00:14:48,855 --> 00:14:51,650
I promised her to bring him
to church tomorrow.

144
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:54,903
If I don't take him, she'll kill me.

145
00:14:55,403 --> 00:14:58,573
If you become a hurdle,
she'll poison your food too.

146
00:14:58,740 --> 00:15:02,869
If he comes to know about this,
he'll kill us.

147
00:15:03,035 --> 00:15:06,663
What is that murmur?
- Nothing, he keeps on blabbering.

148
00:16:18,062 --> 00:16:22,234
Why did you insist I must come here
as if it is very important?

149
00:16:22,442 --> 00:16:25,903
Church...God...
- To wash off the sins committed by us.

150
00:16:26,446 --> 00:16:28,406
The only sin I've committed
is meeting you.

151
00:16:28,572 --> 00:16:29,490
Nothing else.

152
00:16:30,575 --> 00:16:32,826
Where's Das?

153
00:16:37,288 --> 00:16:38,372
Where is Das?

154
00:16:38,539 --> 00:16:40,875
He would've got drunk and
playing cards somewhere.

155
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:43,336
We must reform him!

156
00:16:43,503 --> 00:16:46,589
What's this Chinna?
Strange to see you in church.

157
00:16:46,755 --> 00:16:48,423
Why not ask him directly?

158
00:16:48,591 --> 00:16:49,341
Will you keep shut?

159
00:16:49,509 --> 00:16:52,094
You came here to see me, right?

160
00:16:53,386 --> 00:16:54,429
Did you feel like that?

161
00:16:54,971 --> 00:16:55,680
He brought me here.

162
00:16:55,847 --> 00:16:57,890
Then, why did keep on staring at me?

163
00:16:58,182 --> 00:16:59,350
Staring at you?

164
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,186
I was watching the girls with you.

165
00:17:02,312 --> 00:17:05,690
Had you seen other girls,
I would've cut you to pieces.

166
00:17:05,856 --> 00:17:06,774
You know that, right?

167
00:17:09,109 --> 00:17:11,111
Why are you hitting him?
Look at me!

168
00:17:12,113 --> 00:17:14,490
What you don’t expect may never happen!

169
00:17:14,949 --> 00:17:18,035
What you expect will surely happen!

170
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:19,620
May be he got it!

171
00:17:22,163 --> 00:17:24,499
Why do you hide your feelings?

172
00:17:25,959 --> 00:17:27,168
Look dear...

173
00:17:27,460 --> 00:17:30,837
Don't play with me about
inner and outer feelings.

174
00:17:31,005 --> 00:17:33,466
Before it is dark, go home carefully.

175
00:17:33,632 --> 00:17:34,383
Go.

176
00:17:35,134 --> 00:17:37,051
How long will you escape from me?

177
00:17:39,221 --> 00:17:41,390
Hey...look at me!

178
00:17:42,641 --> 00:17:45,727
I saw it in your eyes now...

179
00:17:48,895 --> 00:17:51,606
Some day you will be mine!

180
00:17:53,526 --> 00:17:54,317
Bye.

181
00:18:00,449 --> 00:18:03,243
Looks like she'll trap you, buddy.

182
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:07,247
How is it possible?
If she thinks so, is it okay?

183
00:18:07,413 --> 00:18:09,499
Nobody can trap you so easily, buddy.

184
00:18:09,664 --> 00:18:10,875
Who Maria is!

185
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:13,418
Why is he looking angrily at me?

186
00:18:19,298 --> 00:18:21,593
Hi Pani! How do you do?

187
00:18:21,759 --> 00:18:23,260
Long time no see.

188
00:18:23,595 --> 00:18:25,096
Are you returning from church?

189
00:18:25,888 --> 00:18:28,473
I don't feel like talking
to any girl in this village.

190
00:18:28,641 --> 00:18:30,643
But I don't know why with you...

191
00:18:31,519 --> 00:18:34,688
I'm going on talking to you
but you're not responding at all.

192
00:18:34,855 --> 00:18:38,525
You must talk to me next time
as I talked to you now.

193
00:18:43,946 --> 00:18:48,033
Brother, if you like any girl,
either you take her as concubine,

194
00:18:48,201 --> 00:18:49,576
or else devastate,

195
00:18:49,743 --> 00:18:52,871
but why are you hesitating about Pani?

196
00:18:53,038 --> 00:18:57,625
All other women are like losing hair.
But Pani is my life.

197
00:18:57,792 --> 00:18:59,377
I must touch only after
making her my wife.

198
00:18:59,545 --> 00:19:01,296
That's why I'm patient.

199
00:19:09,971 --> 00:19:11,681
I'll tell how to trap him.

200
00:19:12,765 --> 00:19:15,434
If mach remains inside box,
can it light fire?

201
00:19:15,851 --> 00:19:17,436
It won't light fire.

202
00:19:17,644 --> 00:19:21,480
Fire is lighted only when stick
is rubbed with the box.

203
00:19:21,647 --> 00:19:22,648
,Got it now?

204
00:19:30,323 --> 00:19:32,240
How much we owe to Dosa Punnamma's?

205
00:19:32,825 --> 00:19:33,409
Rs.100.

206
00:19:33,576 --> 00:19:35,243
Let's clear it today.

207
00:19:37,788 --> 00:19:40,289
Who is Joseph? Never seen him here.

208
00:19:41,040 --> 00:19:42,750
He's new to this area, buddy.

209
00:19:42,917 --> 00:19:44,918
He took loan and refusing to repay.

210
00:19:46,003 --> 00:19:47,588
Where did you get money to give loans?

211
00:19:48,298 --> 00:19:49,507
I can't believe it.

212
00:19:55,429 --> 00:19:58,265
Why did you back off?
- Nothing, buddy.

213
00:20:01,268 --> 00:20:03,687
How far still?
- Near by...next street.

214
00:20:04,645 --> 00:20:06,480
I don't know to which street
I must take him now.

215
00:20:06,647 --> 00:20:08,440
He's killing me with questions.

216
00:20:08,607 --> 00:20:10,734
Buddy, next street.

217
00:20:12,028 --> 00:20:13,278
Just now you said this street.

218
00:20:13,445 --> 00:20:15,196
I'm telling the same thing again, buddy.

219
00:20:19,535 --> 00:20:21,077
I'll tell that again, buddy.

220
00:20:22,871 --> 00:20:23,455
Come.

221
00:20:59,779 --> 00:21:00,529
What?

222
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:03,073
Dreaming about me hugging her!

223
00:21:05,035 --> 00:21:08,162
If you act like a pimp again,
I'll kill you.

224
00:21:08,328 --> 00:21:09,329
Got it?

225
00:21:17,421 --> 00:21:22,259
You talked about match box and stick,
he's dumb like a mud doll.

226
00:21:22,884 --> 00:21:24,928
I'll puncture your back.

227
00:21:32,518 --> 00:21:33,560
Buddy!

228
00:21:34,019 --> 00:21:34,728
Come here.

229
00:21:34,894 --> 00:21:36,020
Coming, buddy.

230
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:39,232
The slap I got morning
is still hurting me.

231
00:21:39,398 --> 00:21:40,941
Don't know what he's up to now?
- Come.

232
00:21:41,942 --> 00:21:43,778
Why did you call me, buddy?

233
00:21:43,944 --> 00:21:47,698
Buddy...that is...
- Tell me, what's it, buddy?

234
00:21:48,282 --> 00:21:49,282
Nothing...

235
00:21:50,410 --> 00:21:51,701
Buddy, my button!

236
00:21:53,119 --> 00:21:53,953
That is...

237
00:21:55,372 --> 00:21:56,373
Tell me now.

238
00:21:58,250 --> 00:21:59,375
That's it.

239
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:00,751
That is...

240
00:22:01,502 --> 00:22:02,378
It came..

241
00:22:02,753 --> 00:22:03,837
What has come?

242
00:22:04,756 --> 00:22:05,548
That thing...

243
00:22:06,633 --> 00:22:09,134
It has come...on her...

244
00:22:09,301 --> 00:22:11,386
Buddy! I knew!

245
00:22:11,554 --> 00:22:12,971
You will get it.

246
00:22:13,138 --> 00:22:14,639
Hold your head high.

247
00:22:14,973 --> 00:22:16,391
I feel shy.

248
00:22:19,144 --> 00:22:22,897
Buddy...will you do me a favour?

249
00:22:23,064 --> 00:22:24,149
Tell me, buddy.

250
00:22:26,401 --> 00:22:28,736
I want to meet her.
- Who?

251
00:22:32,530 --> 00:22:33,406
Tell me.

252
00:22:34,616 --> 00:22:37,411
I must see her...

253
00:22:37,577 --> 00:22:39,495
That's all?
I'll get her right now.

254
00:22:39,663 --> 00:22:43,250
Buddy, not now.

255
00:22:45,250 --> 00:22:47,170
She makes fantastic gravy and rice,

256
00:22:48,337 --> 00:22:51,673
will you ask her to come here with it?

257
00:22:53,968 --> 00:22:55,344
Look, how he's blushing!

258
00:22:56,636 --> 00:23:00,807
Sister! It has worked!

259
00:23:00,973 --> 00:23:04,769
Sister! It has worked!

260
00:23:09,816 --> 00:23:12,817
My son never asked till now,
he asked me to get food for him.

261
00:23:13,486 --> 00:23:15,028
I don't see him here.

262
00:23:18,365 --> 00:23:19,031
He'll come.

263
00:23:20,157 --> 00:23:21,283
I'll leave it here.

264
00:23:21,451 --> 00:23:22,493
He'll come and have it.

265
00:23:23,202 --> 00:23:24,453
He told me to come here, right?

266
00:23:24,746 --> 00:23:25,663
Yes.

267
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:28,832
Would he come here?
- Why did she come here?

268
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:30,125
Where else would he go?

269
00:23:31,335 --> 00:23:33,045
She too has brought food.
- Buddy!

270
00:23:33,336 --> 00:23:34,171
Buddy!

271
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:36,840
He asked me to come here, right?
Why hasn't he turned up yet?

272
00:23:37,007 --> 00:23:38,467
Let him come at anytime,
please sit here.

273
00:23:39,926 --> 00:23:42,721
How was he today morning?

274
00:23:44,722 --> 00:23:45,682
Have you started it again?

275
00:23:45,848 --> 00:23:47,349
It's 50th time now.

276
00:23:47,517 --> 00:23:48,977
Tell me, this is that last time.

277
00:23:49,519 --> 00:23:53,189
When he came out,
the way he was feeling shy...

278
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:55,941
Never seen him like that, trust me.

279
00:23:56,107 --> 00:23:59,235
Infact I too felt embarrassed,
think about it yourself.

280
00:23:59,528 --> 00:24:00,319
Then?

281
00:24:00,569 --> 00:24:03,365
He hung his head feeling shy
thinking about you.

282
00:24:08,452 --> 00:24:09,703
Why hasn't he come yet?

283
00:24:10,579 --> 00:24:11,705
He'll come...wait.

284
00:24:12,248 --> 00:24:13,415
He must come from home, right?

285
00:24:13,582 --> 00:24:16,669
That old woman is there, right?
She'll not even sleep.

286
00:24:16,835 --> 00:24:20,212
She keeps vigil on him like a ghost
fearing some girl may kidnap him.

287
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:23,091
I must gouge out her eyes with ladle.

288
00:24:24,509 --> 00:24:28,387
She thinks the food counter
is some big star hotel.

289
00:24:28,554 --> 00:24:32,432
Only I know the pain of people
eating in her food counter.

290
00:24:32,767 --> 00:24:33,933
I'll take you to task.

291
00:24:34,101 --> 00:24:35,311
Be patient.

292
00:24:35,810 --> 00:24:37,895
This will carry on few more days only.

293
00:24:39,105 --> 00:24:43,108
As soon as I go to that home,
I'll shut down the food counter immediately.

294
00:24:43,359 --> 00:24:47,863
Do that first, at least for this
I'll unite you with him.

295
00:24:48,905 --> 00:24:53,952
Keep watching the scene, the old woman must
come wagging like dog for food after me.

296
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:56,120
I'll hit you with slippers.
How dare you talk like that!

297
00:24:56,288 --> 00:24:57,122
Bloody girl!

298
00:24:57,288 --> 00:25:01,209
My son knows about you,
that's why he told me to bring food for him.

299
00:25:01,375 --> 00:25:02,877
Come...come...
- Stop...stop...

300
00:25:03,044 --> 00:25:04,963
Stop, you girl.

301
00:25:05,130 --> 00:25:06,673
Stop...stop...

302
00:25:07,006 --> 00:25:09,717
How dare you try to trap my son!

303
00:25:09,884 --> 00:25:13,471
If you look at my son,
I'll gouge out your eyes!

304
00:25:13,636 --> 00:25:14,137
Get lost!

305
00:25:17,057 --> 00:25:21,103
Buddy..it seems he'll cheat me
into going to church,

306
00:25:21,269 --> 00:25:24,939
and take me around the streets
for collecting a never given loan,

307
00:25:25,105 --> 00:25:28,776
and imagine Pani as his sister
like in the film 'Raktha Sambandham'.

308
00:25:29,861 --> 00:25:33,155
Hey buffalo! You won't anything
silly like this again, right?

309
00:25:36,909 --> 00:25:38,826
Nephew! Can I ask you a question?

310
00:25:38,993 --> 00:25:41,663
Why not ask 5 or 6?

311
00:25:42,329 --> 00:25:44,249
I'm serious, why are you doing comedy?

312
00:25:44,415 --> 00:25:45,500
Don't get angry.

313
00:25:45,666 --> 00:25:47,999
Come on, ask me.

314
00:25:48,752 --> 00:25:52,298
That girl is yearning to be
yours since childhood.

315
00:25:52,464 --> 00:25:54,174
Why are you rejecting her?

316
00:25:58,929 --> 00:26:02,641
You've grown old but not wise.

317
00:26:08,770 --> 00:26:10,940
Ever since my father went to sea
with Yesupadam and died,

318
00:26:11,106 --> 00:26:13,067
Seal has been accusing them of it,

319
00:26:14,317 --> 00:26:15,860
6how can she accept this girl?

320
00:26:17,488 --> 00:26:21,199
Even if I go against her and marry her,
can she live happily there?

321
00:26:22,325 --> 00:26:24,411
Let's allow them be happy like that.

322
00:26:27,704 --> 00:26:29,624
Sea is there for all my life.

323
00:26:31,541 --> 00:26:34,211
If you want to share drinks
happily, do join me.

324
00:26:34,377 --> 00:26:36,462
If you want to talk about this,
then go to bed silently.

325
00:26:36,630 --> 00:26:37,423
Got it?

326
00:26:39,258 --> 00:26:40,759
I'm scared you may hit me!

327
00:26:41,009 --> 00:26:41,884
Will you hit me?

328
00:26:42,885 --> 00:26:43,970
Go to sleep.

329
00:27:09,911 --> 00:27:11,621
Special news bulletin about weather…

330
00:27:11,787 --> 00:27:17,418
Fishermen are advised not to venture
into sea for 48 hours...

331
00:27:17,584 --> 00:27:20,545
It seems your man has gone to sea.

332
00:27:21,380 --> 00:27:23,089
Does he have sense?

333
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:27,426
Are you up?

334
00:27:28,010 --> 00:27:30,053
What brings you here in so heavy rain?

335
00:27:30,221 --> 00:27:35,392
Heavy winds and rains, yet he ventured
into sea with his friends.

336
00:27:35,558 --> 00:27:36,601
What are you saying?

337
00:27:36,769 --> 00:27:38,895
Inform Yesupadam about it.

338
00:27:41,105 --> 00:27:41,856
Sir...

339
00:28:02,459 --> 00:28:04,794
Where you my King?

340
00:28:10,674 --> 00:28:13,844
Dusk has fallen...

341
00:28:35,321 --> 00:28:37,990
The food has gone cold...

342
00:28:46,332 --> 00:28:49,669
My heart is sinking...

343
00:28:50,545 --> 00:28:54,673
If you're with me...

344
00:28:59,178 --> 00:29:01,054
The sky will be bright...

345
00:29:01,221 --> 00:29:04,348
Today you're not with me...

346
00:29:07,018 --> 00:29:15,358
My heart is broken...
heart is broken...

347
00:29:19,195 --> 00:29:22,240
What am I to do, my King?

348
00:29:24,784 --> 00:29:27,954
I'm aimless...

349
00:29:31,624 --> 00:29:33,584
Why are you sitting distraught here?

350
00:29:33,875 --> 00:29:35,920
Missing fishermen have returned safely.

351
00:29:36,086 --> 00:29:38,463
Boat got damaged, that's all.

352
00:29:47,888 --> 00:29:49,890
Lost honour, buddy.

353
00:29:50,724 --> 00:29:53,560
Damaged Yesupadam's boat.

354
00:29:53,685 --> 00:29:56,230
Entire village saw this, buddy.

355
00:30:01,233 --> 00:30:04,612
Buddy...buddy...

356
00:30:08,490 --> 00:30:09,491
Lost honour, right?

357
00:30:15,079 --> 00:30:16,414
Don't you dare come with me again!

358
00:30:16,582 --> 00:30:17,499
Go alone.

359
00:30:20,836 --> 00:30:24,506
Lost honour...
Maria is shameless man, right?

360
00:30:25,173 --> 00:30:26,508
I don't have any honour, right?

361
00:30:36,892 --> 00:30:40,562
You went away as you like...

362
00:30:40,936 --> 00:30:43,355
I almost died waiting for your return.

363
00:30:44,398 --> 00:30:46,275
You know there's cyclone,
why did you enter sea?

364
00:30:55,241 --> 00:30:56,117
Go away silently.

365
00:31:00,454 --> 00:31:01,288
What do you think of yourself?

366
00:31:01,455 --> 00:31:03,123
I don't think of anything.

367
00:31:07,045 --> 00:31:07,670
What?

368
00:31:08,962 --> 00:31:09,922
Love?

369
00:31:11,965 --> 00:31:12,882
Empty ground!

370
00:31:14,134 --> 00:31:15,134
Mind your work.

371
00:31:22,476 --> 00:31:23,727
You're alive, right?

372
00:31:26,479 --> 00:31:27,605
I've seen you, right?

373
00:31:29,606 --> 00:31:30,357
Get lost.

374
00:31:30,732 --> 00:31:31,567
Go away.

375
00:31:31,733 --> 00:31:32,359
Get lost!

376
00:32:17,942 --> 00:32:19,860
Got match stick?

377
00:32:24,449 --> 00:32:26,618
Got match stick?
- No.

378
00:32:32,957 --> 00:32:33,624
What?

379
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:35,125
Got match stick?

380
00:32:36,210 --> 00:32:37,169
Got it.

381
00:32:51,848 --> 00:32:54,768
Take match box.
He'll never reform.

382
00:32:56,060 --> 00:32:56,978
You carry on.

383
00:32:57,520 --> 00:32:58,688
Found him for free.

384
00:33:13,536 --> 00:33:19,458
Sea and love...it's always new
any number of times you see.

385
00:33:19,708 --> 00:33:20,584
What do you say?

386
00:33:22,376 --> 00:33:25,046
Hey old man!
Looks like you're in mood for it.

387
00:33:25,212 --> 00:33:28,423
I'm telling you with my experience.

388
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:29,800
Experience?

389
00:33:30,093 --> 00:33:32,678
If you've experience,
how is that you're a bachelor?

390
00:33:32,845 --> 00:33:37,682
Love is heart must always hit
the coast like waves.

391
00:33:37,849 --> 00:33:39,433
That will give you strength.

392
00:33:41,185 --> 00:33:45,939
For a man who wishes to succeed,
a woman must be there in his life.

393
00:33:46,106 --> 00:33:48,942
That's okay,
who is the woman in your life?

394
00:33:49,109 --> 00:33:51,903
Buddy! Did you hear the old man?

395
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:54,531
It seems a woman must be
there in a man's life.

396
00:33:54,698 --> 00:33:56,200
Stop it.

397
00:34:11,213 --> 00:34:16,969
My dear new couple...in the presence
of Lord and friends...

398
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:47,802
Pani! Girls of your age are getting married,
when are you getting married?

399
00:35:49,137 --> 00:35:52,556
Just say okay, let's marry immediately.

400
00:36:17,246 --> 00:36:19,706
Don't you know whose bike that is?

401
00:36:19,873 --> 00:36:20,749
Move.

402
00:36:25,711 --> 00:36:28,172
If you're feeling so itchy,
rub yourself into some thorny bush.

403
00:36:28,463 --> 00:36:30,423
Why are you rubbing ladies' slippers?

404
00:36:39,099 --> 00:36:43,519
If say loudly what I said now,
people would laugh at you,

405
00:36:44,271 --> 00:36:46,439
so, what you will do in future is,

406
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:50,610
if you come to church,
don't misbehave with girls,

407
00:36:50,775 --> 00:36:51,777
behave properly!

408
00:37:18,427 --> 00:37:20,679
What bothers you if he
touches Pani's slippers?

409
00:37:22,514 --> 00:37:24,432
You like her so much,
why do you hide it?

410
00:37:25,016 --> 00:37:26,434
You love Pani, buddy.

411
00:37:29,603 --> 00:37:31,062
You'll get the sick instead of him.

412
00:37:33,148 --> 00:37:34,900
This is what you get for telling truth.

413
00:37:47,911 --> 00:37:50,080
Stop Pani.

414
00:37:50,498 --> 00:37:51,499
Please listen to me.

415
00:37:51,831 --> 00:37:53,625
Wait a minute, Pani.
- What's it?

416
00:37:53,793 --> 00:37:56,711
Maria...
- Why? Forget it.

417
00:37:56,836 --> 00:37:57,463
Stop.

418
00:37:58,005 --> 00:37:58,922
I don't want this trouble anymore.

419
00:37:59,088 --> 00:38:00,715
Please listen to me.

420
00:38:02,717 --> 00:38:03,677
What?

421
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:05,677
Listen to me,

422
00:38:05,844 --> 00:38:09,681
I'm happy with choir singing,
going to church and offering prayers.

423
00:38:09,849 --> 00:38:12,101
He told there's nothing
in him for me, right?

424
00:38:12,268 --> 00:38:12,976
Why again?

425
00:38:13,143 --> 00:38:16,562
No, only I know how much he loves you.

426
00:38:16,730 --> 00:38:20,025
Yes...would anyone hit the girl he loves?

427
00:38:20,192 --> 00:38:23,195
Listen to me.
He grew up like that.

428
00:38:24,195 --> 00:38:28,865
He loves you, that's why he had a fight
with dark man for touching your slippers.

429
00:38:29,032 --> 00:38:30,034
Do you know that?

430
00:38:35,873 --> 00:38:36,874
What did you say?

431
00:38:37,750 --> 00:38:39,751
Go, ask him.

432
00:38:58,893 --> 00:38:59,769
I saw you, right?

433
00:39:01,563 --> 00:39:02,981
You're alive, right?

434
00:39:14,240 --> 00:39:16,242
You like her so much,
why do you hide it?

435
00:39:17,619 --> 00:39:18,996
You love Pani.

436
00:39:23,250 --> 00:39:28,253
For a man who wishes to succeed,
a woman must be there in his life.

437
00:39:38,931 --> 00:39:41,682
Some day you will be mine.

438
00:41:27,362 --> 00:41:28,489
Why so late?

439
00:41:28,655 --> 00:41:30,449
I had to prepare food.

440
00:41:32,034 --> 00:41:35,704
Though I warn my heart refuses to listen...

441
00:41:35,871 --> 00:41:39,791
Even in dream I think about you only...

442
00:41:40,125 --> 00:41:40,876
What?

443
00:41:43,378 --> 00:41:46,631
Annagaru's romance is rocking,
he's sensational.

444
00:41:48,048 --> 00:41:51,427
There's power in first love...

445
00:41:51,594 --> 00:41:55,722
And you know that well...

446
00:41:55,931 --> 00:42:02,896
Dreams are murmuring...
My heart is swinging...

447
00:42:03,063 --> 00:42:04,230
Isn't it sensational, buddy?

448
00:42:07,733 --> 00:42:09,485
Buddy...buddy...

449
00:42:09,985 --> 00:42:10,694
Take it.

450
00:42:21,954 --> 00:42:25,666
The time girl has come seeking me...

451
00:42:25,833 --> 00:42:28,001
When she stands away from me...

452
00:42:37,427 --> 00:42:44,768
Without your order
I can't even take breathe...

453
00:42:57,237 --> 00:43:00,449
Hey Yesupadam! Come out!

454
00:43:00,614 --> 00:43:05,119
My son is NTR but
your daughter is not Savithri.

455
00:43:08,121 --> 00:43:10,790
If you've shame and shy, come out.

456
00:43:13,251 --> 00:43:14,753
Hey little devil!

457
00:43:14,961 --> 00:43:16,963
Didn't you find any other man in town?

458
00:43:17,130 --> 00:43:18,757
Did you find my only my son?

459
00:43:18,923 --> 00:43:19,800
Come out I say!

460
00:43:19,967 --> 00:43:22,510
What? Why are you going overboard?

461
00:43:22,677 --> 00:43:25,889
If I come to know if you're
after my son or talk to him,

462
00:43:26,054 --> 00:43:28,640
I'll throw you into sea, mind it.

463
00:43:28,807 --> 00:43:29,891
Why are you staring at me?

464
00:43:30,059 --> 00:43:31,644
Why are you all watching fun?

465
00:43:32,061 --> 00:43:34,313
Fight between daughter-in-law
and mother-in-law is common.

466
00:43:34,480 --> 00:43:35,105
Isn't it?

467
00:43:35,271 --> 00:43:38,817
I'll cut your tongue.

468
00:43:38,983 --> 00:43:40,818
Who is your mother-in-law?

469
00:43:40,985 --> 00:43:42,862
Why are you asking as if you don't know?

470
00:43:43,028 --> 00:43:43,655
You!

471
00:43:43,822 --> 00:43:46,074
Have you gone that far?

472
00:43:46,240 --> 00:43:52,413
If you enter my home as daughter-in-law,
I'll cut your legs.

473
00:43:53,581 --> 00:43:56,000
Go now, let's think about that
after marriage.

474
00:43:56,166 --> 00:43:58,126
Are you planning marriage also?

475
00:43:58,293 --> 00:44:00,671
Let me see, how you'll marry him!

476
00:44:00,836 --> 00:44:04,548
I know who is responsible for this,
let Maria come.

477
00:44:04,715 --> 00:44:08,219
Is any record dance going
here to watch? Go away.

478
00:44:08,385 --> 00:44:09,262
Get lost.

479
00:44:09,429 --> 00:44:13,014
Go...have come to watch...go away.

480
00:44:13,181 --> 00:44:15,683
Today, he's dead in my hands.

481
00:44:30,697 --> 00:44:35,952
Love story between a famous
film star and...

482
00:44:40,164 --> 00:44:41,958
What are you doing here?

483
00:44:42,918 --> 00:44:47,297
If there's not a woman in house,
did you see how shabby the home is?

484
00:44:47,463 --> 00:44:48,464
Don't you wash clothes?

485
00:44:48,630 --> 00:44:51,550
If Seal sees you, you're gone.
Go.

486
00:44:52,217 --> 00:44:55,971
Your name is Maria,
you're afraid of Seal.

487
00:44:56,304 --> 00:44:59,223
She'll wake up entire village.
What am I to do now?

488
00:44:59,432 --> 00:45:01,518
She has already done it.

489
00:45:02,768 --> 00:45:04,228
Announcement is also over.

490
00:45:06,481 --> 00:45:07,398
What do you want?

491
00:45:10,233 --> 00:45:11,652
Will you give whatever I ask?

492
00:45:13,528 --> 00:45:16,030
It depends on what you ask...

493
00:45:16,197 --> 00:45:17,449
What if you ask more...

494
00:45:18,242 --> 00:45:21,577
Would I ask for a child?

495
00:45:23,121 --> 00:45:24,581
You may ask that also.

496
00:45:25,164 --> 00:45:25,789
Go.

497
00:45:27,625 --> 00:45:28,710
Shall I go?

498
00:45:33,755 --> 00:45:34,797
Shall I go?

499
00:45:52,856 --> 00:45:54,608
You said empty ground.

500
00:45:57,652 --> 00:45:59,153
You own it now, right?

501
00:45:59,695 --> 00:46:00,404
Go.

502
00:46:26,179 --> 00:46:30,974
Why don't you be with me
for some more time?

503
00:46:31,141 --> 00:46:35,645
Why are you leaving urgently?

504
00:46:57,875 --> 00:47:03,922
Before our talk drop like rain
and hearts sprout out...

505
00:47:04,088 --> 00:47:08,467
Please don't go away from me...

506
00:47:08,635 --> 00:47:20,354
If you vanish like lightning,
I'll remain in darkness...

507
00:47:46,460 --> 00:47:56,803
With an unseen net,
you trapped my heart...

508
00:47:56,969 --> 00:48:07,020
Blowing unheard whistle,
you made my heart to tremble...

509
00:48:07,188 --> 00:48:12,485
Come to me like a wave...

510
00:48:12,652 --> 00:48:17,697
Shall I become a bangle on your hand?

511
00:48:17,864 --> 00:48:23,244
Late is nectar...
learn to be patient...

512
00:48:23,411 --> 00:48:29,583
Nectar is bitter and
your word is sweet...

513
00:48:31,585 --> 00:48:36,506
You've to wait for some more time...

514
00:48:36,673 --> 00:48:41,010
What's so urgent for you?

515
00:49:13,581 --> 00:49:15,708
Why are you wearing these
clothes for fishing?

516
00:49:15,876 --> 00:49:16,710
Are you not coming for fishing?

517
00:49:16,876 --> 00:49:18,753
I told you to go alone, right?
Go.

518
00:49:18,920 --> 00:49:20,963
That's it, why would you need us now?

519
00:49:21,130 --> 00:49:21,757
Carry on.

520
00:49:21,922 --> 00:49:31,640
I'll wait for you like the
ever lasting sea water...

