00:49:31,806 --> 00:49:42,483
The anger on my face is
unknown hurdle for you...

522
00:49:42,650 --> 00:49:48,071
Even in salty winds,
I can taste sweetness...

523
00:49:48,239 --> 00:49:53,077
Let's cover ourselves with
the warmth of hot wind...

524
00:49:53,244 --> 00:49:58,582
The fish smell on your body is
fragrance of flowers to me in my arms...

525
00:49:58,748 --> 00:50:05,504
Talk all the night and
hunt me with your words...

526
00:50:27,525 --> 00:50:33,572
You're the eyelid of my eyes…
You're the father of my kids...

527
00:50:33,739 --> 00:50:38,452
Our kids must sing and
dance like waves...

528
00:50:38,619 --> 00:50:46,209
Your words will come true...
you and me would we...

529
00:50:46,376 --> 00:50:50,546
Let's drown ourselves
in the sea of love...

530
00:50:53,548 --> 00:50:54,842
Why are you surprized?

531
00:50:55,009 --> 00:50:58,344
If we've come to your house
seeking girl, you must be very lucky.

532
00:50:58,512 --> 00:51:01,306
My elder brother
who refused to marry till now,

533
00:51:01,472 --> 00:51:05,393
today he wants to marry
only Pani no one else.

534
00:51:13,900 --> 00:51:15,985
How long will you ponder, Yesupadam?

535
00:51:16,362 --> 00:51:20,032
You took loan from me years ago.
I didn't care about it.

536
00:51:20,197 --> 00:51:22,701
4Keep it as gift and give your
daughter in marriage to me.

537
00:51:22,867 --> 00:51:25,661
Marriage for money!

538
00:51:25,994 --> 00:51:29,623
Sister insisted, so I came
seeking hand traditionally.

539
00:51:29,791 --> 00:51:31,584
If not I would've kidnapped her.

540
00:51:52,936 --> 00:51:54,355
What's wrong with him?

541
00:52:03,445 --> 00:52:09,493
Okay...just because Chinna went away...

542
00:52:15,331 --> 00:52:17,291
You always hit only me.

543
00:52:17,708 --> 00:52:20,294
I can hit only you.
Who else can I hit?

544
00:52:21,713 --> 00:52:22,756
Okay, don't get angry.

545
00:52:26,467 --> 00:52:28,469
I should've killed and
thrown your body in sea.

546
00:52:28,635 --> 00:52:31,471
Just because I left you,
are you acting like a hero here?

547
00:52:37,311 --> 00:52:40,856
Hey dark man! I don't have anyone.

548
00:52:42,273 --> 00:52:43,817
The people I have one of them died.

549
00:52:44,483 --> 00:52:45,567
I can't lose her.

550
00:52:45,735 --> 00:52:47,070
Why are you still talking to him, Maria?

551
00:52:47,237 --> 00:52:49,072
I expected you'd hit him.

552
00:52:50,155 --> 00:52:50,989
You calm down.

553
00:52:52,074 --> 00:52:54,117
Sir, please don't.

554
00:52:54,326 --> 00:52:56,077
A girl's life would get ruined.

555
00:52:56,244 --> 00:52:59,413
Pay my money or give me your daughter.

556
00:55:04,945 --> 00:55:06,697
Go...go away...

557
00:55:06,864 --> 00:55:09,199
This is my family problem,
don't interfere.

558
00:55:09,367 --> 00:55:10,326
Go away!

559
00:55:18,916 --> 00:55:19,875
Come...come...

560
00:55:20,043 --> 00:55:22,878
Come...come...

561
00:55:23,213 --> 00:55:24,714
Come...come...

562
00:55:49,362 --> 00:55:58,327
Yesupadam, my loan with interest must
reach my home by tomorrow evening.

563
00:55:58,494 --> 00:56:01,831
If not you'll not live.

564
00:56:18,847 --> 00:56:19,932
Threatened Yesupadam...

565
00:56:32,400 --> 00:56:34,110
He warned him to pay up.

566
00:56:37,989 --> 00:56:39,407
Don't know what Yesupadam would do?

567
00:57:02,137 --> 00:57:03,638
Hello...please, come in.

568
00:57:07,057 --> 00:57:08,226
Two years contract.

569
00:57:08,393 --> 00:57:12,188
First year salary will be
adjusted with advance.

570
00:57:12,396 --> 00:57:15,858
You'll get only the second year's salary.

571
00:57:16,025 --> 00:57:19,068
If you're not happy with job,
you can't quit midway.

572
00:57:19,235 --> 00:57:21,445
You're going to Sudan.
You know that, right?

573
00:57:21,905 --> 00:57:23,490
Sign the agreement.

574
00:57:47,135 --> 00:57:50,347
Seal was telling you all these years,
good sense prevailed on you now.

575
00:58:05,862 --> 00:58:07,488
Settle the dark man's loan.

576
00:58:11,826 --> 00:58:14,619
Don't take it as for him, it was Pani.

577
00:58:17,121 --> 00:58:18,498
Take care of her.

578
00:58:20,500 --> 00:58:26,047
You were born in sea...
you grew up in sea...

579
00:58:27,673 --> 00:58:31,844
How can you leave this place? How?

580
00:58:42,728 --> 00:58:43,812
Just 2 years only!

581
00:58:44,981 --> 00:58:46,316
No problem, bye.

582
00:59:25,226 --> 00:59:31,023
You were living happily with sea
and your friends.

583
00:59:32,190 --> 00:59:36,152
Because of me...because of me...

584
00:59:39,530 --> 00:59:42,701
Not because of you...it was for you.

585
00:59:50,373 --> 00:59:51,541
Don't cry.

586
00:59:59,382 --> 01:00:00,174
Don't cry.

587
01:00:07,389 --> 01:00:09,141
Will you send me off with tears?

588
01:00:29,159 --> 01:00:30,243
Just 2 years only.

589
01:00:31,369 --> 01:00:32,413
It'll fly away.

590
01:00:48,844 --> 01:00:50,303
I'll be back at the wink of an eye.

591
01:01:29,215 --> 01:01:31,592
I didn't have the courage that day
to turn back and see her face.

592
01:01:33,552 --> 01:01:34,970
2 years have passed.

593
01:01:36,304 --> 01:01:40,891
I'll go home and see my Pani
in person not in a photo.

594
01:01:41,018 --> 01:01:43,019
Are you sad, buddy?

595
01:01:45,938 --> 01:01:47,856
His lover is waiting for him back home.

596
01:01:48,023 --> 01:01:49,775
My good friend has left her there.

597
01:01:49,942 --> 01:01:51,485
Will you please stop it?

598
01:01:52,235 --> 01:01:53,820
Do you've lover back home?

599
01:01:57,157 --> 01:01:58,033
Wife?

600
01:01:58,659 --> 01:02:00,494
You'd have escaped from her.

601
01:02:00,661 --> 01:02:02,162
It seems he's married.

602
01:02:02,329 --> 01:02:06,499
He's not a happy bachelor like us.

603
01:03:49,677 --> 01:03:51,262
From Andhra!

604
01:04:13,239 --> 01:04:15,742
This is Lord Venkateswara's dollar.

605
01:06:03,967 --> 01:06:06,052
Where are we now?

606
01:06:44,378 --> 01:06:45,380
What?

607
01:06:45,547 --> 01:06:48,925
Nothing...he said sizes have changed.

608
01:06:49,092 --> 01:06:50,425
Will it fit him?

609
01:06:51,219 --> 01:06:56,557
Forget it, if he eats your cooking,
he'll get back to shape.

610
01:07:08,358 --> 01:07:10,527
Sister!
- Come in.

611
01:07:10,695 --> 01:07:12,530
Sister!
- I'm here.

612
01:07:15,199 --> 01:07:16,700
Got two calls from Africa, sister.

613
01:07:16,867 --> 01:07:18,494
Don't know what it is, come quickly.

614
01:07:18,659 --> 01:07:19,327
When?

615
01:07:28,085 --> 01:07:31,296
I'm Williams here, Maria's colleague.

616
01:07:32,130 --> 01:07:32,922
Where is he?

617
01:07:33,090 --> 01:07:36,385
I called you to tell something.

618
01:07:36,552 --> 01:07:37,302
Go ahead.

619
01:07:37,469 --> 01:07:43,474
Few workers in my company have
been kidnapped by terrorists.

620
01:07:43,641 --> 01:07:46,143
We don't have any information
about them till now.

621
01:07:46,311 --> 01:07:48,980
We suspect Maria is also among them.

622
01:07:49,146 --> 01:07:49,896
What are you saying?

623
01:07:50,063 --> 01:07:54,902
You don't worry, Sudan government
is trying to rescue them.

624
01:07:55,068 --> 01:07:56,402
Nothing will happen to them.

625
01:07:56,570 --> 01:07:57,112
You...

626
01:08:44,322 --> 01:08:47,199
Give it to me...

627
01:08:55,582 --> 01:08:59,961
Tell him to give me...I'm hungry.

628
01:09:02,963 --> 01:09:04,298
Tell him to give.

629
01:09:20,354 --> 01:09:25,484
Yesterday...she was there...

630
01:09:27,110 --> 01:09:31,364
I was also there with her...

631
01:09:34,033 --> 01:09:35,243
I...

632
01:09:52,259 --> 01:09:55,095
I was there...

633
01:10:06,396 --> 01:10:17,908
Millions of stars in the sky showered
light when you were with me...

634
01:10:29,210 --> 01:10:36,425
She filled my heart with honey
and happiness..

635
01:11:00,488 --> 01:11:06,994
She entwined me like a plant...

636
01:11:41,693 --> 01:11:58,958
My heart...my thoughts are
filled with you...

637
01:11:59,126 --> 01:12:07,634
Till yesterday sorrow wasn't
a part of my life...

638
01:12:07,966 --> 01:12:17,016
It was your breathe I felt in
the jingle of my bangles...

639
01:12:17,184 --> 01:12:23,856
O time, go back and get her for me...

640
01:13:03,350 --> 01:13:09,940
Waves of tears are rolling for you...

641
01:13:12,109 --> 01:13:19,240
It's waiting eagerly for arrival...

642
01:16:02,097 --> 01:16:04,016
Sir, we sent him trusting you, right?

643
01:16:04,768 --> 01:16:06,185
We can find a job for a man.

644
01:16:07,020 --> 01:16:09,063
Can we guard his entire life?

645
01:16:09,229 --> 01:16:14,609
Forget about your guarding duty,
you sent him there, right?

646
01:16:14,944 --> 01:16:15,736
Answer me.

647
01:16:16,362 --> 01:16:19,072
Look, I sent him on his mother's request.

648
01:16:19,238 --> 01:16:21,866
Ask his mother or
the company where he works.

649
01:16:22,033 --> 01:16:23,952
I don't have anything do with it.

650
01:18:14,220 --> 01:18:15,054
Bloody...

651
01:18:44,538 --> 01:18:45,414
Bloody...

652
01:18:47,875 --> 01:18:49,167
Bloody mad men!

653
01:18:51,170 --> 01:18:52,212
What do you want?

654
01:18:53,046 --> 01:18:54,214
What do you want?

655
01:18:58,342 --> 01:18:59,219
Money?

656
01:19:00,052 --> 01:19:00,970
We don't have.

657
01:19:03,847 --> 01:19:05,641
Neither you have nor do I!

658
01:19:06,266 --> 01:19:07,559
Can't you see it?

659
01:19:13,356 --> 01:19:14,774
All we've is just life.

660
01:19:15,650 --> 01:19:17,277
Take that also, bloody!

661
01:19:21,948 --> 01:19:22,449
What?

662
01:19:33,626 --> 01:19:34,668
Fire!

663
01:19:38,005 --> 01:19:38,630
Come.

664
01:19:40,340 --> 01:19:40,966
Come.

665
01:19:43,801 --> 01:19:44,927
They'll not kill me.

666
01:19:45,677 --> 01:19:46,804
They need money, right?

667
01:20:01,777 --> 01:20:04,445
If you cut my legs and
ask me to dance...

668
01:20:04,612 --> 01:20:08,365
If you strangle my neck
and ask me to sing...

669
01:20:11,159 --> 01:20:13,496
If you cut my wings and
ask me to fly...

670
01:20:13,662 --> 01:20:16,832
Sorrow in my heart is turning
into erupting lava...

671
01:20:21,252 --> 01:20:25,340
I'm a hunter who hunts in sea...

672
01:20:25,506 --> 01:20:29,384
I'm the king of sea...

673
01:20:30,011 --> 01:20:34,098
I spill blood to fish out pearls...

674
01:20:34,265 --> 01:20:39,269
Maria is the king of sea...

675
01:20:42,354 --> 01:20:50,612
If they make prawn gravy,
I'm on moon...

676
01:20:50,863 --> 01:20:55,200
Salted fish curry is mouth watering...

677
01:20:55,367 --> 01:21:00,122
The intoxication will last for a day...

678
01:21:00,454 --> 01:21:09,087
I've put lid on the volcano
of anger for you...

679
01:22:28,911 --> 01:22:35,292
I'm singing alone before
people with stone hearts...

680
01:22:41,965 --> 01:22:47,971
I'm struggling between
these heartless people...

681
01:22:50,722 --> 01:22:54,810
I came alone to a strange country,
I was living like a corpse here...

682
01:22:54,976 --> 01:23:01,315
I lost my sense living with the
hope of uniting with you...

683
01:25:05,430 --> 01:25:09,517
Sir, I'm AOC worker Maria here.

684
01:25:11,851 --> 01:25:13,770
Yes, I'm Maria.

685
01:25:14,563 --> 01:25:16,190
Where are you, Maria?

686
01:25:18,399 --> 01:25:21,694
Sir...want money.

687
01:25:22,612 --> 01:25:24,447
They're shooting people here, sir.

688
01:25:25,073 --> 01:25:27,200
I don't get what you say!

689
01:25:27,324 --> 01:25:29,577
Yes Pani, it's me.

690
01:25:31,787 --> 01:25:32,788
I'm alive.

691
01:25:38,292 --> 01:25:40,252
I don't know how long I will be alive!

692
01:25:41,337 --> 01:25:43,881
What? What did you say now?

693
01:25:44,716 --> 01:25:47,302
Yes sir...help sir...

694
01:25:50,095 --> 01:25:52,806
I don't get what you're saying, Maria.

695
01:25:58,270 --> 01:26:00,147
Yes, it's me...tell me...

696
01:26:02,148 --> 01:26:04,234
I don't know if I can see you again or not.

697
01:26:05,693 --> 01:26:07,362
Please don't say like that.

698
01:26:08,195 --> 01:26:09,905
I don't get what you say!

699
01:26:14,409 --> 01:26:16,953
Where are you? Please tell me that.
Where are you?

700
01:26:19,914 --> 01:26:23,251
No sir...I don't know, sir.

701
01:26:33,927 --> 01:26:35,304
It's all over, Pani.

702
01:26:35,470 --> 01:26:37,388
Why are you talking like this?

703
01:26:39,682 --> 01:26:43,353
You...don't wait for me.

704
01:26:51,193 --> 01:26:52,278
Listen to me carefully.

705
01:26:52,653 --> 01:26:53,988
Nothing will happen to you.

706
01:26:54,154 --> 01:26:55,113
Nothing will happen to you.

707
01:26:55,613 --> 01:26:56,989
Yes sir...

708
01:26:58,992 --> 01:27:01,536
Speaking...speaking...

709
01:27:04,122 --> 01:27:05,539
You're my husband.

710
01:27:05,998 --> 01:27:07,791
Nobody can separate us.

711
01:27:16,507 --> 01:27:18,092
I'll wait for your return.

712
01:27:29,561 --> 01:27:31,396
Can you hear me, Maria?

713
01:27:59,256 --> 01:28:05,929
Hello brother! Kill me right now!

714
01:28:07,095 --> 01:28:11,099
If not you'll regret for it later.

715
01:28:16,688 --> 01:28:19,065
I've informed Pani, it's over.

716
01:28:20,233 --> 01:28:21,068
Over!

717
01:28:42,753 --> 01:28:43,712
What happened?

718
01:28:43,880 --> 01:28:45,172
What did they do with you?

719
01:28:48,551 --> 01:28:50,303
I was scared without you.

720
01:29:07,652 --> 01:29:08,653
How, buddy?

721
01:29:24,542 --> 01:29:25,543
Let's go from here.

722
01:29:26,418 --> 01:29:29,505
Yes, let's go from here.

723
01:29:29,921 --> 01:29:31,006
Let's go.

724
01:29:36,677 --> 01:29:37,679
Where is he?

725
01:29:39,680 --> 01:29:41,265
It's all over, Pani.

726
01:29:42,600 --> 01:29:44,560
Don't wait for me.

727
01:29:45,686 --> 01:29:49,439
Don't cry...don't cry...

728
01:29:49,981 --> 01:29:56,279
Don't cry, Maria...

729
01:30:05,954 --> 01:30:08,041
Come...come...

730
01:30:08,791 --> 01:30:10,333
Come.

731
01:30:15,881 --> 01:30:18,550
I don't know if this mother's
love can bring him,

732
01:30:19,676 --> 01:30:23,471
but I'm confident your love will
surely bring him back.

733
01:33:56,375 --> 01:33:59,336
You're coming...you're coming...

734
01:34:10,595 --> 01:34:14,015
Yesupadam...Yesupadam...

735
01:34:17,895 --> 01:34:21,356
Maria is coming....he's coming...

736
01:34:22,524 --> 01:34:26,444
Yesupadam, he's coming!

737
01:34:28,070 --> 01:34:29,363
He's coming!

738
01:34:47,796 --> 01:34:50,465
Maria is coming...Maria is coming...

739
01:34:50,632 --> 01:34:51,634
Who told you?

740
01:34:52,092 --> 01:34:53,510
I'm telling!

741
01:34:57,096 --> 01:34:58,431
I made inquiry.

742
01:34:58,765 --> 01:34:59,975
He'll never come.

743
01:35:03,435 --> 01:35:04,311
He'll come.

744
01:35:05,814 --> 01:35:07,315
He'll never come.

745
01:35:07,606 --> 01:35:08,858
I'll come.

746
01:35:19,493 --> 01:35:21,328
You humiliated me here, right?

747
01:35:22,119 --> 01:35:25,832
I'm like fire, what will you do now?

748
01:35:27,625 --> 01:35:28,583
Are you laughing?

749
01:35:29,001 --> 01:35:32,128
Laugh...hasn't your pride come down yet?

750
01:35:38,676 --> 01:35:41,095
I should've taken you to task
that day itself.

751
01:35:43,222 --> 01:35:45,516
You can't do anything, you dog.

752
01:35:45,682 --> 01:35:47,476
Are you calling me a dog?

753
01:35:50,354 --> 01:35:51,771
Can't I do anything?

754
01:35:54,358 --> 01:35:55,693
Can't I do anything?

755
01:36:06,368 --> 01:36:08,371
If Maria can't get me,
nobody else can get me.

756
01:36:08,537 --> 01:36:09,788
I'll kill you.

757
01:36:18,462 --> 01:36:19,547
Will you kill me?

758
01:36:20,716 --> 01:36:22,551
Okay, take it...kill me.

759
01:36:22,716 --> 01:36:23,717
Kill me I say!

760
01:36:34,395 --> 01:36:42,319
Yesupadam...Maria is coming.

761
01:36:42,484 --> 01:37:45,042
Maria is coming....he's coming.

762
01:45:46,734 --> 01:45:52,198
When cyclones of fire hits...

763
01:45:52,864 --> 01:45:57,994
When the snow clad mountains of mercy melts...

764
01:45:58,662 --> 01:46:04,208
When injustice touches the sky...

765
01:46:04,376 --> 01:46:09,672
When humans lose humanity....

766
01:46:10,506 --> 01:46:15,594
When life is strained by tyranny...

767
01:46:15,761 --> 01:46:21,016
Your love will not stop...

768
01:46:22,100 --> 01:46:27,771
My heart get going...
my heart get going...

769
01:46:33,903 --> 01:46:39,949
You get up and run...

770
01:46:40,117 --> 01:46:46,079
Love will never end...

771
01:46:58,091 --> 01:47:09,602
Though our skies are different...
Though our hopes are shattered...

772
01:47:09,769 --> 01:47:21,445
Though youth has changed...
Though you've forgotten me...

773
01:47:21,613 --> 01:47:26,659
Even if world loses status...

774
01:47:26,826 --> 01:47:32,414
Your love won't stop....

775
01:48:08,698 --> 01:48:14,787
Don't get afraid or scared...
Your sorrows are yesterday's tales...

776
01:48:14,994 --> 01:48:17,288
We're new born...

777
01:48:17,456 --> 01:48:20,375
Your words are cool like moonbeam...

778
01:48:20,542 --> 01:48:26,213
Your love will stand test of time...

779
01:48:26,381 --> 01:48:30,968
In a fraction of second it vanished...

780
01:49:06,833 --> 01:49:09,252
My Maria promised to come
at the wink of an eye.

781
01:49:10,755 --> 01:49:12,506
I'm living for you only.

782
01:49:13,756 --> 01:49:18,094
Come back...I must bear your child.

783
01:49:19,220 --> 01:49:20,846
It must play with waves.

784
01:49:22,349 --> 01:49:23,600
We must watch it.

785
01:49:24,600 --> 01:49:27,228
Come back quickly....come...

786
01:49:28,770 --> 01:49:29,521
Come!

787
01:49:32,024 --> 01:49:32,900
Come.

788
01:49:34,443 --> 01:49:35,277
Come.

789
01:51:06,860 --> 01:51:07,653
Mother!

790
01:51:16,328 --> 01:51:16,995
Mother!

791
01:55:37,067 --> 01:55:37,943
It's sea!

792
01:57:39,470 --> 01:57:42,306
Where you my King?

793
01:57:47,729 --> 01:57:50,773
Dusk has fallen...

794
01:58:06,996 --> 01:58:09,414
The food has gone cold...

795
01:58:12,417 --> 01:58:15,712
My heart is sinking...

796
01:58:16,712 --> 01:58:21,259
If you're with me...

797
01:58:22,426 --> 01:58:30,100
The sky will be bright...

798
01:58:33,229 --> 01:58:35,939
Today you're not with me...

799
01:58:36,105 --> 01:58:42,444
My heart is broken...
heart is broken...

800
01:59:03,047 --> 01:59:07,260
Eyes are searching for eyelids...

801
01:59:07,426 --> 01:59:10,595
Sea of tears rolling down...

802
01:59:10,762 --> 01:59:12,765
Body won over life...

803
01:59:12,931 --> 01:59:15,600
Moment stood still like eon...

804
01:59:15,768 --> 01:59:17,728
Where you my King?

805
01:59:21,564 --> 01:59:25,317
What am I to do, my king?

806
01:59:28,029 --> 01:59:36,328
I'm living for you only...

807
01:59:40,832 --> 01:59:44,002
For 21 days I was held
captive by the Sudan militia.

808
01:59:44,252 --> 01:59:47,672
For 9 days I ran over 300 kilometres
without food and water.

809
01:59:48,547 --> 01:59:51,007
I lost my friend Chinna in sea.

810
01:59:51,466 --> 01:59:52,801
Lost Swamy in desert.

811
01:59:53,844 --> 01:59:55,846
I overcame every hurdle
to come back alive.

812
01:59:56,305 --> 01:59:57,347
For my Pani!

813
02:00:07,064 --> 02:00:08,982
Now only I'm breathing.

814
02:00:09,692 --> 02:00:11,109
You're my breathe.

